user & server


user --> server
    * login
    * logoff
    * status
server --> user
    * online
    * offline
user --> user
    * direct message
    * broadcast message

commands:

     login <user> <password>
     logoff

     msg <user>  body....
     guest: "msg jim Hello World" <-- sent
     jim: "msg guest Hello World" <-- recv


     #topic <-- chatroom / group chat
     join #topic
     leave #topic
     send: msg #topic body...
     recv: msg #topic:<login> body ...

